# Gmail Account
IMAPAccount philliptvo
Host imap.gmail.com
Port 993
User phillip.t.vo@gmail.com
PassCmd "gpg -qd ~/.isync/isync_philliptvo.gpg"
SSLType IMAPS
AuthMechs LOGIN
CertificateFile /usr/local/etc/openssl/cert.pem

IMAPStore philliptvo-remote
Account philliptvo

MaildirStore philliptvo-local
Path ~/Mail/philliptvo/
Inbox ~/Mail/philliptvo/INBOX
Subfolders Verbatim

Channel philliptvo
Master :philliptvo-remote:
Slave :philliptvo-local:
Create Both
Expunge Both
Patterns * !"[Gmail]/All Mail" !"[Gmail]/Important" !"[Gmail]/Starred" !"[Gmail]/Bin"
SyncState *

# UWaterloo Account
IMAPAccount ptgvo
Host imap-mail.outlook.com
Port 993
