MaildirStore ptgvo-local
Path ~/Mail/ptgvo/
Inbox ~/Mail/ptgvo/INBOX
Subfolders Verbatim

Channel ptgvo
Master :ptgvo-remote:
Slave :ptgvo-local:
Create Both
Expunge Both
Patterns *
SyncState *
